Package lwon.data

Class Dictionary

java.lang.Object
lwon.data.DataObject
lwon.data.Dictionary
public class Dictionary extends DataObject
A mapping from string keys to (possibly multiple) DataObject values. The same key may appear multiple times in a dictionary, and is bound to a list of each of the values it is associated with, in the same order.
